                <div id="content">

                        <p class="highlight" id="desc">BLAST finds regions of similarity between biological sequences.
                        <a id="moreHelp" class="helplink hiding" title="help" href="#">more...</a>
                        </p>
                        <div class="helpbox hidden" toggle="moreHelp">
The Basic Local Alignment Search Tool (BLAST) finds regions of	local
similarity between sequences. The program compares nucleotide or
protein	sequences to sequence databases and calculates the statistical
significance of matches. BLAST can be used to infer functional and
evolutionary relationships between sequences as well as help identify
members of gene families.
</div>

                        <!-- <iframe id="RSIFrameNoRes" class="ifrm"  align="middle" name="RSIFrame"  noresize="noresize" frameborder="0" border="0" cellspacing="0" scrolling="no" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0"  
                        src="plinkcgi.cgi?CMD=Get&OPL=BlastHomeAd"></iframe> -->
                        
                        <a target="_self" title="Cobalt Multiple Alignment Tool" href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/tools/cobalt/cobalt.cgi?link_loc=BlastHomeAd">
