                        </a>

                        <h2>BLAST Assembled RefSeq Genomes</h2>

						<div id="genomes" class="section">
<p>Choose a species genome to search, or 
<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/mapview/" id="listall" title="BLAST other genome">list all genomic BLAST databases</a>.
</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/genome/seq/BlastGen/BlastGen.cgi?taxid=9606" title="BLAST human genome">Human</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/genome/seq/BlastGen/BlastGen.cgi?taxid=10090" title="BLAST mouse genome">Mouse</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/genome/seq/BlastGen/BlastGen.cgi?taxid=10116" title="BLAST rat genome">Rat</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/genome/seq/BlastGen/BlastGen.cgi?taxid=3702" title="BLAST arabidopsis genome"><i>Arabidopsis thaliana</i></a></li>
</ul>
<ul class="genomesMiddle">
<li><a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/genome/seq/BlastGen/BlastGen.cgi?taxid=4530" title="BLAST rice genome"><i>Oryza sativa</i></a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/genome/seq/BlastGen/BlastGen.cgi?taxid=9913" title="BLAST cow genome"><i>Bos taurus</i></a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/genome/seq/BlastGen/BlastGen.cgi?taxid=7955" title="BLAST zebra fish genome"><i>Danio rerio</i></a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/genome/seq/BlastGen/BlastGen.cgi?taxid=7227" title="BLAST fruit fly"><i>Drosophila melanogaster</i></a></li>
